p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">GameStop=E2=80=99s ecommerce str=
ategy has faltered, its bricks-and-mortar store count is shrinking and its =
sales are in a multiyear slide. But one measure of the video game retailer =
is a picture of health: the amount of cash in its accounts.</p><p style=3D"=
margin: 16px 0;">The company at the centre of the 2021 meme-stock frenzy ha=
