th on little more than the re-emergence of the influential social media fan=
 known as Roaring Kitty.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Management t=
ook advantage of its sudden increase in valuation to sell 45mn shares and r=
aise $933mn. Last Friday GameStop alerted investors to a potential sale of =
another 75mn shares, which at Monday=E2=80=99s closing price would be worth=
 $1.9bn.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In doing so, the company followed =
a well-worn meme stock playbook of recent years, using their shortlived pop=
ularity to raise cash. The mystery is where it will put all the money, whic=
h stands at $2bn.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That $2 bill=
ion, though, is before <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/c=
