it sold them for, bank probably hundreds of millions of dollars of profit a=
nd support the stock price.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Repeat=
 this every year or so and you have a profitable business of selling stock =
to people during moments of euphoria and buying it back cheaply when they l=
ose interest.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Never mind the video=
games.</li></ol><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This is so stupid, I=E2=80=99m=
 sorry. This can=E2=80=99t really work. Except that it can? This, I suppose=
